Kai?

137
00:09:37.610 --> 00:09:38.711  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kai!

138
00:09:41.314 --> 00:09:42.615  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ow!

139
00:09:43.215 --> 00:09:44.317  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei grunting]

140
00:09:46.586 --> 00:09:48.020  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[man] Damn, no signal.

141
00:09:48.788 --> 00:09:50.990  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Kei] A... A car...
[man] Huh?

142
00:09:51.057 --> 00:09:52.792  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Please call an ambulance.

143
00:09:53.693 --> 00:09:55.261  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
He's human!

144
00:09:57.363 --> 00:09:58.998  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[man] That's your own fault.

145
00:10:06.005 --> 00:10:08.174  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] <i>Is it my fault?</i>

146
00:10:11.043 --> 00:10:13.312  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>If I hadn't asked Kai for help...</i>

147
00:10:14.380 --> 00:10:16.616  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>maybe this wouldn't have happened.</i>

148
00:10:17.617 --> 00:10:19.619  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[man] Stand up, walk!

149
00:10:21.220 --> 00:10:23.022  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Damn, he can't stand.

150
00:10:27.126 --> 00:10:29.195  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] <i>No, that's wrong.</i>

151
00:10:29.996 --> 00:10:33.065  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>If it weren't for this guy,</i>
<i>Kai would be fine.</i>

152
00:10:35.001 --> 00:10:36.302  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>If it weren't for...</i>

153
00:10:36.369 --> 00:10:38.037  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>If it weren't for...</i>

154
00:10:38.804 --> 00:10:40.773  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>If it weren't for him!</i>

155
00:10:42.908 --> 00:10:43.776  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[both grunting]

156
00:10:57.223 --> 00:10:58.357  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] Kai.

157
00:10:58.991 --> 00:11:00.259  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Thank God.

158
00:11:00.826 --> 00:11:02.261  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I was just playing dead.

159
00:11:02.828 --> 00:11:04.830  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It doesn't even hurt.

160
00:11:05.197 --> 00:11:06.232  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[chuckling]

161
00:11:09.101 --> 00:11:10.670  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Okay, let's go.

162
00:11:10.970 --> 00:11:12.772  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
We'll take this guy's bike.

163
00:11:14.206 --> 00:11:15.841  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kei?

164
00:11:20.112 --> 00:11:21.113  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[groans]

165
00:11:22.214 --> 00:11:25.017  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I think this is it.

166
00:11:25.084 --> 00:11:27.186  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What do you mean?

167
00:11:28.988 --> 00:11:30.923  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I think my leg's broken.

168
00:11:30.990 --> 00:11:33.893  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
And look what happened
when it got a little bright.

169
00:11:33.959 --> 00:11:36.062  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-And if we're together...
-Kei.

170
00:11:37.029 --> 00:11:40.433  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-People and Ajins shouldn't be together--
-Kei.

171
00:11:40.866 --> 00:11:42.334  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You're human.

172
00:11:43.836 --> 00:11:45.304  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
That's how I see it.

173
00:11:46.138 --> 00:11:48.974  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
So, if we can make it to a place
no one else knows,

174
00:11:49.442 --> 00:11:51.177  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
then you're still human.

175
00:11:53.345 --> 00:11:55.815  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hold on. I'll treat your leg.

176
00:11:58.984 --> 00:12:00.186  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] <i>No.</i>

177
00:12:00.953 --> 00:12:02.388  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>No!</i>

178
00:12:02.455 --> 00:12:04.890  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>All of this has made</i>
<i>one thing clear to me.</i>

179
00:12:05.458 --> 00:12:08.094  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>I'm not human anymore!</i>

180
00:12:09.328 --> 00:12:10.229  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kai grunts]

181
00:12:10.996 --> 00:12:13.032  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kai] Ow, ow...

182
00:12:15.000 --> 00:12:18.737  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Kei] <i>Even if I tell him to leave me,</i>
<i>I don't think he'll listen.</i>

183
00:12:19.238 --> 00:12:22.942  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>With this broken leg,</i>
<i>I'll be putting Kai in danger.</i>

184
00:12:23.876 --> 00:12:26.145  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>What do I do? What should I do?</i>

185
00:12:26.912 --> 00:12:29.215  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Think, as an...</i>

186
00:12:30.316 --> 00:12:32.118  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>As an Ajin.</i>

187
00:12:43.395 --> 00:12:45.064  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kei! Don't!

188
00:12:52.271 --> 00:12:53.772  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kei...

189
00:12:57.409 --> 00:13:00.045  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'm all healed. Let's go, Kai.

190
00:13:08.787 --> 00:13:10.256  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Aw, lost again.

191
00:13:11.423 --> 00:13:16.262  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Damn it, shouldn't have gone
for the long shot.

192
00:13:17.129 --> 00:13:19.431  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[man 1] It seems they're afraid...

193
00:13:20.533 --> 00:13:23.302  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
that a lot of people will die again.

194
00:13:25.938 --> 00:13:30.376  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Or maybe they're afraid of another case
like Shinya Nakamura's.

195
00:13:30.442 --> 00:13:33.512  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
So, they aren't making any bold moves.

196
00:13:34.513 --> 00:13:37.483  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[man 2] So, Mr. Sato,
what are you going to do now?

197
00:13:39.285 --> 00:13:42.388  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I have to show him the way.

198
00:13:43.956 --> 00:13:45.558  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'm going to meet Kei Nagai.

199
00:13:46.058 --> 00:13:48.427  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Will you help, Tanaka?

200
00:13:50.462 --> 00:13:53.232  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kei Nagai, huh?

201
00:14:12.351 --> 00:14:13.886  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
So...

202
00:14:13.953 --> 00:14:15.354  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'm an Ajin.

203
00:14:16.488 --> 00:14:18.123  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Are you really okay?

204
00:14:18.190 --> 00:14:19.225  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Huh?

205
00:14:19.959 --> 00:14:21.126  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What do you mean?

206
00:14:21.193 --> 00:14:23.462  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I know it was bad,
but you crossed a line.

207
00:14:25.331 --> 00:14:26.632  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'm fine.

208
00:14:27.233 --> 00:14:28.634  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I've calmed down.

209
00:14:28.901 --> 00:14:30.569  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-And my head's clear.
-That's not--

210
00:14:30.636 --> 00:14:33.572  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'm more worried about you, Kai.

211
00:14:34.039 --> 00:14:34.907  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Huh?

212
00:14:35.274 --> 00:14:38.410  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
When humans die,
they can't come back to life.

213
00:14:42.548 --> 00:14:44.016  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
So, what now?

214
00:14:46.151 --> 00:14:47.386  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hey.

215
00:14:49.154 --> 00:14:52.258  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
The police will be able
to trace the location.

216
00:14:52.658 --> 00:14:55.094  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
So, it's just junk now.

217
00:14:58.597 --> 00:15:00.266  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Anyway,

218
00:15:00.332 --> 00:15:02.501  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I want to go somewhere safe, I guess.

219
00:15:03.969 --> 00:15:07.172  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Kai] If you want a safe place,
we could just stay on this mountain.

220
00:15:07.606 --> 00:15:11.110  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
When we run out of food or clothes,
I can go get more.

221
00:15:13.679 --> 00:15:15.147  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It's true that last year

222
00:15:15.214 --> 00:15:18.284  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
there were 2396 people involved
in mountain accidents.

223
00:15:18.350 --> 00:15:22.187  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
And 294 of them either died
or were never found.

224
00:15:24.456 --> 00:15:26.225  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You know all that?

225
00:15:26.292 --> 00:15:28.060  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It was on the news.

226
00:15:28.127 --> 00:15:31.430  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
If almost 300 people disappear
in the mountains every year.

227
00:15:31.497 --> 00:15:33.399  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Then maybe I won't be found.

228
00:15:33.699 --> 00:15:36.335  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-So...
-But it won't work.

229
00:15:36.969 --> 00:15:37.703  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Huh?

230
00:15:39.171 --> 00:15:42.341  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I want to live a quiet, normal life.

231
00:15:45.611 --> 00:15:50.115  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I don't want to have my normal life taken
from me just because I'm an Ajin.

232
00:15:52.418 --> 00:15:54.253  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Kyushu.
-Huh?

233
00:15:54.320 --> 00:15:56.588  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
My grandpa lives in Kyushu.

234
00:15:56.655 --> 00:16:00.192  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
It's a small country village,
so no one there would care.

235
00:16:00.726 --> 00:16:03.195  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-I mean...
-That I'm an Ajin...?

236
00:16:04.430 --> 00:16:07.032  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'm sure you could live peacefully there.

237
00:16:09.301 --> 00:16:10.569  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You're right.

238
00:16:10.636 --> 00:16:12.504  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
That's probably the best plan.

239
00:16:12.571 --> 00:16:14.740  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Okay, it's decided.

240
00:16:15.741 --> 00:16:17.710  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'll run to the store.

241
00:16:17.977 --> 00:16:19.511  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You want anything?

242
00:16:19.578 --> 00:16:21.447  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
How about a toothbrush?

243
00:16:21.513 --> 00:16:22.681  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Okay.

244
00:16:34.226 --> 00:16:36.328  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Apparently, they lost the man in the hat.

245
00:16:37.162 --> 00:16:40.466  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
But he probably won't do anything
too conspicuous yet.

246
00:16:40.532 --> 00:16:44.436  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Raising the stakes right now is risky
for him, too.

247
00:16:44.770 --> 00:16:46.505  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Then what do we do now?

248
00:16:46.572 --> 00:16:48.640  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I have that meeting.

249
00:16:48.707 --> 00:16:52.111  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
The committee members are fussy
about time and money.

250
00:16:54.246 --> 00:16:56.715  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Question her. I leave it to you.

251
00:16:58.250 --> 00:16:59.651  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Keep your composure.

252
00:16:59.718 --> 00:17:02.755  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
And remember not to spill any information.

253
00:17:03.022 --> 00:17:04.323  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yes, sir.

254
00:17:11.196 --> 00:17:12.798  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] <i>A village in Kyushu...</i>

255
00:17:14.199 --> 00:17:16.668  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Humans who won't mind an Ajin...</i>

256
00:17:20.072 --> 00:17:21.707  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>People like that don't exist.</i>

257
00:17:22.775 --> 00:17:26.412  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>And it's 600 miles to Kyushu.</i>
<i>There's no way we could make it.</i>

258
00:17:26.478 --> 00:17:30.115  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>It'd be hard enough as an Ajin,</i>
<i>but it's too dangerous for a human.</i>

259
00:17:32.317 --> 00:17:35.220  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
This is as far as I go with Kai.

260
00:17:37.790 --> 00:17:38.824  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[electricity crackling]

261
00:17:39.291 --> 00:17:40.325  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps]

262
00:17:42.227 --> 00:17:43.362  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What is...?

263
00:17:45.764 --> 00:17:48.167  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
This is as far as I go with Kai.

264
00:17:57.709 --> 00:17:59.778  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[woman] I don't know his accomplice!

265
00:17:59.845 --> 00:18:03.449  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
And besides,
other detectives were here last night!

266
00:18:03.515 --> 00:18:05.350  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'm not a police officer.

267
00:18:05.417 --> 00:18:07.553  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'm with the Ajin Control Commission.

268
00:18:07.619 --> 00:18:11.156  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
The Commission aims to research
and manage Ajins--

269
00:18:11.223 --> 00:18:12.424  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I don't care!

270
00:18:12.491 --> 00:18:16.195  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I just want to ask you
about Kei Nagai's private life.

271
00:18:16.261 --> 00:18:17.563  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
So, why do I...

272
00:18:17.629 --> 00:18:20.132  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
have to deal with all this stuff?

273
00:18:20.432 --> 00:18:23.402  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Because you're Kei Nagai's younger sister.

274
00:18:24.303 --> 00:18:25.437  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Eriko.

275
00:18:26.405 --> 00:18:29.475  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I'm sorry to bother you
during your recovery,

276
00:18:29.541 --> 00:18:30.876  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
but I appreciate your cooperation.

277
00:18:32.845 --> 00:18:34.113  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Gross.

278
00:18:34.179 --> 00:18:34.847  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Huh?

279
00:18:35.414 --> 00:18:40.385  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
To think there was one in my family
who thought he was a human. It's gross.

280
00:18:42.588 --> 00:18:46.225  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
